===Etymology===
:from the Latin and Greek word ''metaphora'', which means the transferring of the meaning of one word to another word.

===Noun===
#a [[figure of speech]] in which one word is used to refer to something that it isn't. A similarity is implied.

:''Compare'' [[simile]].
